      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle. This car is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks; the original factory paint remains as vibrant as the day it was delivered. Inside, the cabin serves as a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions with factory-spec precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, chronologically organized service history, showing all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. We have recently performed a full preventative fluid service and a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure the engine and transmission operate flawlessly. This is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
